    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8390647>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Bayesian consensus tree of mtDNA (analysis 2 in Methods: Phylogenetic analysis). Annotations as in Fig. 4." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8390647/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8390651>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Bayesian consensus tree of concatenated matrix (analysis 3) as in Fig. 6 with branches proportional to lengths. Outgroups are cartooned. Concepts of genera as revised in this work appear on relevant branches. Photographed representatives of each genus appear to the right of the tree (Supp. Table 3)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8390651/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8390657>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Habitus comparison between A. O. canadensis and B. O. noveboracensis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8390657/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8390659>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Distributions of O. canadensis and O. noveboracensis showing peripatry. Inset details O. noveboracensis type locality. Lower right detail: habitus of O. noveboracensis-like phenotype from southwestern extreme of range." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8390659/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

